  "slug": "arky-environment",
  "title": "Arky's Environment",
  "description": "Arky's Environment - add new plants, decorations and other things in the world of Minecraft. Unlike many mods, it will not add many of their biomes, rather the opposite will try to improve the old.",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Arky's Environment&nbsp;adds new plants, decorations and other things in the world of Minecraft. Unlike many mods, it will not add many of their biomes, rather the opposite will try to improve the old.<br /><br />This mod was cancelled and remade as a new mod called&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/arky-aesthetics\">Arky's Aesthetics</a></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Subscribe on mod's platforms:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/TpP4vAMDgb\">Discord Server</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@unknownraccooneternaltales4940\">YouTube</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a title=\"Telegramm channel\" href=\"https://t.me/eternal_tales_news\">Telegram channel</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://eternaltales.wiki.gg/wiki/Eternal_Tales_Wiki\">Wiki</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://vk.com/eternal_tales\">VK (Russian)&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://sun9-40.userapi.com/impg/_65N_kgiyOY7Ym8IgH5vCtBw7xcP8shUuOJTOQ/Lu27CXO-MMI.jpg?size=1056x553&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=fb58576d2a11b1402fdfce9eb1996a6a&amp;type=album\" width=\"1042\" height=\"546\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Content:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Biomes:</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Sakura Grove</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-63.userapi.com/impg/X6fHlMV4ndjsUHVZGAAghMKOygqUlRRTqHlSOg/Fy8qXAyNXZE.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=30388814ea93c303a5eaf88bb99f5a1c&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"678\" />Maple Forest</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-39.userapi.com/impg/mWOZBKzqqTUpCPD4p6PjzVYogoHsMi9YKfpbzw/LnONhnDABtA.jpg?size=911x482&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=c8bfebc76d65cbbde7a31afc2eb195ae&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1111\" height=\"588\" />Rocky Desert</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-51.userapi.com/impg/FXJgtXP684joFp1lOupDLnUpSqNW_Jm7B8RRFw/a6jpNzrTvMc.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=12ebf2a9dfdf0309a69ed6eff2cfccf2&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" />Lush Desert&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-64.userapi.com/impg/7fjVvRtDib9jV3_pgfKeoRSYMQCdyJbhdAZzNQ/6T5E7sCBDqo.jpg?size=911x482&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=a05cebfbbc350754d4dc32a8e76c8f9d&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"589\" />Cold Swamp</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-42.userapi.com/impg/VErBFtjEGtZ_RpK27Vf815ZblvtIgf9Xxl_S4g/7klIzo9eCK8.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=72bd8064be4511dd74b824289ed1de50&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Mobs</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Thorny Devil (spawns in Badlands)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-64.userapi.com/impg/Bd7etvVdZdqwEFUcvfMQLIOi1WSaw02T5F6Bxg/ARZWwu6gqdY.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=87de34d2cc992a6f83f190110ef061d7&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Meerkat (spawns in Deserts)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-41.userapi.com/impg/_Mu64VGeDQ8p1iLNFbTEZBrYa3PLC7qBil6jLw/msJkG-37CpE.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=b107a06d6036ff0277b06745329ad2ae&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Glutton (spawns in Swamps and Flower Forest)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">He can eat most of animal types and jump 2 blocks high.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-11.userapi.com/impg/JGJoZLS6zMZ1C8vuxWMqgHigD7Yeufb6spLZyw/vEyu6foTgKA.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=176a76787d7599e81b72a04ecb07db27&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" />Heron (spawns in Swamp)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Eat slimes, gluttons and all fish types except pufferfish</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-50.userapi.com/impg/1Tph-AmYRQXArhWi2fYCn22pfZdvHb_vQ_zNWg/tR5W362idH0.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=067345b0927868cd2451020b2e0e8bdb&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" />Ant Lion (spawns in Ant Lion Nest structure in Deserts)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Very strenght mob.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-85.userapi.com/impg/JSqYMjm-bgnXCrUmOvLA30jO6aTalAugqv8OWQ/aQZ2ITa_lRM.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=7404308179fbfd52f0307cba171d59bc&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></span></p>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Structures</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Swamp Pyramid</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-8.userapi.com/impg/Sfy9LKQ_UiAl36yB7aBayYfuzm_6_S29o5TnfA/E6NHfEBjO7A.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=53c904b19fee4197339dae162f15e322&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" />Frozen Fortress (in Cold Swamp)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-23.userapi.com/impg/1En4bPKvRjMfiUIY-H76r1c3iYl8Eq8p3Lkqxw/MjPRcoJFdM4.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=cf23724faa0ebeee0365bb65be0a675a&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"678\" /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Giant Flower</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-39.userapi.com/impg/mua-JlF9fu_wmPvbHQZMG4eBcv1stTNqzdZSwA/D30NBW1S_rE.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=511d0bf2a773afd660c70ccf37251711&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></span></p>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Other</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Scented Candles.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Adds potion effects for nearest mob in 3 block radius.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/774218471260553236/869005020861972480/unknown.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"634\" />New Teracotta Blocks</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://sun9-54.userapi.com/impg/aJJduL1sYDX5Y-bapKFgjEL16gzYRbHjE-78Ng/SGdNMd5QGg8.jpg?size=1280x678&amp;quality=96&amp;sign=603012023a7814a571e0e13789f37cf3&amp;type=album\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>",
